AetherTune

This project is original MIT-licensed scaffold code generated for a free/open-source music application. It does not include proprietary app code, copyrighted media assets, private API credentials, or DRM circumvention code.

The optional LRCLIB adapter uses LRCLIB's documented public search API at runtime. No LRCLIB lyrics database or lyrics content is bundled with AetherTune. A user-selected result is stored locally with provider attribution. Third-party lyrics remain the property of their respective rightsholders/providers and may be subject to separate terms and local law.
